&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As one of Turnkey’s earliest sales leaders, you’ll own team development, coaching, and performance for a pod of up to 10 sellers. You will help shape the foundation of the sales organization, strengthen the outbound and pipeline motion, and partner cross-functionally with leadership to refine the go-to-market strategy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and mentor a team of AEs and BDRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive consistent attainment across mid-market and enterprise segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build repeatable, scalable sales processes as Turnkey enters its next growth stage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with leadership to refine segmentation as pipeline matures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure pipeline quality, strong forecasting discipline, and predictable execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with marketing and product to strengthen market traction.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create clear promotion paths and manage career growth across pods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a culture of accountability, collaboration, and high performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for a high-EQ people leader who has already proven themselves as a strong Sales Manager and is ready to step into a Senior Sales Manager/ Director scope.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7+ years of sales leadership experience managing AEs (mid-market and/or enterprise) and ideally BDRs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record building and leading high-performing sales teams in fast-growth environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong coaching instincts and high EQ; able to elevate underperformers and accelerate top talent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience operating in an early-stage, unstructured environment where playbooks are still being built.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable managing pipeline, forecasting, segmentation, and process improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work cross-functionally with Product, Marketing, and Leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Motivated by autonomy, ownership, and helping build a sales org from the ground up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A builder at heart—you enjoy creating scalable systems, not just running existing ones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Located in the NYC area and open to hybrid work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re an active participant in the crypto ecosystem, staying on top of emerging trends and protocols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience selling and leading enterprise and mid-market teams across fintech verticals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
